<body>
An invocation that encases the sorcerer in a protective layer of dark<br>
magic.  The sorcerer's body transforms to that of the dead.  Due to the<br>
thickening of skin and stiffening of the limbs, the spell also slightly<br>
reduces the caster's dexterity.  This is a self only spell.<br>
